							<a href="supplyOrderDeal.do?type=repeatCharge&supplyOrderId=$!supplyOrder.id" class="btn btn-mini btn-danger" onclick="return confirm('是否确认对供货单： $!supplyOrder.id 做失败补充操作，操作前请务必核实是供货失败')">失败补充</a>
